# CONTACT FORM

### Submit a contact form
POST http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "subject": "Asking for scholarship",
  "message": "I would like to know more about your services."
}

### Get all contact form submissions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact

### Get a contact form submission by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE

### Update a contact form submission
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "message": "Updated message."
}

### Delete a contact form submission
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE


