### AUTHENTICATION
### =====================

### Google OAuth Login
# This will redirect to Google's login page
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/google

### Google OAuth Callback
# This endpoint will be called by Google after successful authentication
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/google/callback

### Verify Google Authentication Token
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/google/verify
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here